  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0in 5.75pt 0in 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Ardiluses are enorm=
ous
  silicon-based invertebrates. They appear as amorphous semi-transparent bl=
obs,
  with trailing red tendrils.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Their preferred hab=
itat is the
  upper atmosphere of Gas Giant planets. However an Ardilus is capable of
  freely roaming the galaxy. They have a unique ability to travel through h=
yper
  space. Thus they can hyperjump between systems.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>While they typically move quite slowly, Ardiluses ca=
n also
  lunge at amazing speed when any prey is nearby. <span style=3D'mso-no-pro=
of:
  yes'>Ardiluses are very </span>robust and can absorb a great deal of batt=
le
  damage before dying.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Do not start a fight with an Ardilus unless you bring
  overwhelming force to the encounter.</p>
